Welcome to SurvivalSpeed !!!

We hope you will have a good and fun time here, But that is only possible if everyone follows our rules, you can find our rules in the 'Rules' tab in this menu.

We also have a Discord, its full of information you may need. every event or special happening will be reported there ! so make sure youre in it!!!

If you are intrested in other game servers, we offer other games too... just join our Discord to get direct connect links to all our servers we offer !
